        <item>
            <title>OneNotch 0.1.1 (5)</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <p>Faster clipboard workflows directly from the notch.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Navigate items with the Left, Right, Up, and Down arrow keys.</li>
                    <li>Jump to items with Command+1, Command+2, and additional number shortcuts.</li>
                    <li>See rich image previews for copied website links.</li>
                    <li>Sort clipboard items and delete them directly from the notch.</li>
                    <li>Signed with Developer ID and notarized by Apple.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
